items.text: Adam's Delights most ordered dish: S$6 Mee Goreng Special (Combo includes fried egg, cheesy fries & braised mutton). Wholesome meal, yumz, especially with braised mutton & fresh non-spicy green chilli
Noo Cheng Adam Road Big Prawn Noodle not recommend. With the same price can have much better one......
Hey, if you wanna order food from Selamat Datang stall, do order from the Pacik instead of the Macik. He gave more then the Macik. :)
Try the NASI LEMAK!
One of the best indian rojak and the only one in Adam Road
Crayfish from Adam Seafood BBQ is excellent!

Indian-muslim mutton soup is nice
Nasi Lemak and Ice Jelly best here.
Tech Kee Hot & Cold Dessert has the best Sweet Potato Soup!

Prawn noodle, tau suan & 猪脚炒米粉.... Freaking yummy!!!
